title: Snaps -Brian Kelly & LSU stunned vs. Florida State, Playoff expansion, Week 1 takeaways
itunes:title: Snaps -Brian Kelly & LSU stunned vs. Florida State, Playoff expansion, Week 1 takeaways
description:
T-Bob Hebert and Aaron Murray discuss LSU's shocking loss vs. Florida State, whether Tiger fans should press the panic button on Brian Kelly, and if College Football Playoff expansion will be good for the sport. Later, the two share their overall takeaways from a wild week 1 and Aaron lists his top 5 quarterbacks of the weekend featuring Ohio State's CJ Stroud, Florida's Anthony Richardson, Georgia's Stetson Bennett, Oklahoma State's Spencer Sanders, and Florida State's Jordan Travis. #Herd
